  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个用户创建新笔记的完整流程图。场景是：用户在浏览器里点击\"Nova Nota\"按钮，然后输入内容并提交。涉及三个参与者：用户、浏览器和服务器。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "user",
        "browser",
        "server",
        "Nova Nota"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了。用户点击按钮后，浏览器应该给用户展示一个文本输入框对吧？然后用户输入内容时，浏览器要实时显示出来？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "user",
        "browser",
        "campo de texto"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，这两个交互都是用户和浏览器之间的。接下来用户点击\"Submit\"按钮，这时候浏览器要向服务器发送POST请求，地址是helsinki那个exampleapp的notes接口。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "user",
        "browser",
        "Submit",
        "POST",
        "exampleapp/notes"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我已经添加了从浏览器到服务器的POST请求箭头。我在服务器旁边加了个注释，说明\"O servidor processa a nova nota\"，同时把服务器激活了。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "browser",
        "server",
        "POST",
        "activate server",
        "Note"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "服务器处理完后，需要返回确认信息给浏览器，然后服务器就可以释放了。接下来浏览器要做两件事：先更新本地笔记列表，然后向服务器请求最新的完整数据。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "server",
        "browser",
        "Confirmação",
        "deactivate server",
        "Atualiza",
        "GET"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "确认一下：浏览器自己更新列表是一个自循环箭头对吧？然后GET请求是到data.json获取JSON格式的数据？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "browser-browser",
        "GET",
        "data.json"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "没错。服务器再次激活，返回更新后的笔记列表，然后释放。最后浏览器把新笔记展示给用户看。",
      "elements_involved": [
